&lt;p&gt;For the record, this was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3554&quot; title=&quot;Hints are not replayed unless node was marked down&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3554&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3554&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I think we should try to make sure we use generics for Range object now as this would typically have caught this one.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
